optimized_sql: WITH date_cte AS (SELECT d_date_sk FROM date_dim WHERE d_year = 2001 AND d_moy = 11), addr_cte AS (SELECT ca_address_sk FROM customer_address WHERE ca_gmt_offset = -6), hd_cte AS (SELECT hd_demo_sk FROM household_demographics WHERE hd_buy_potential LIKE '1001-5000%'), cd_cte AS (SELECT cd_demo_sk, cd_marital_status, cd_education_status FROM customer_demographics WHERE (cd_marital_status = 'M' AND cd_education_status = 'Unknown') OR (cd_marital_status = 'W' AND cd_education_status = 'Advanced Degree')), customer_cte AS (SELECT c.c_customer_sk, cd.cd_marital_status, cd.cd_education_status FROM customer c INNER JOIN cd_cte cd ON c.c_current_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk INNER JOIN addr_cte a ON c.c_current_addr_sk = a.ca_address_sk INNER JOIN hd_cte h ON c.c_current_hdemo_sk = h.hd_demo_sk), fact_cte AS (SELECT cr.cr_call_center_sk, cr.cr_net_loss, cust.cd_marital_status, cust.cd_education_status FROM catalog_returns cr INNER JOIN date_cte d ON cr.cr_returned_date_sk = d.d_date_sk INNER JOIN customer_cte cust ON cr.cr_returning_customer_sk = cust.c_customer_sk) SELECT cc.cc_call_center_id AS Call_Center, cc.cc_name AS Call_Center_Name, cc.cc_manager AS Manager, SUM(f.cr_net_loss) AS Returns_Loss FROM fact_cte f INNER JOIN call_center cc ON f.cr_call_center_sk = cc.cc_call_center_sk GROUP BY cc.cc_call_center_id, cc.cc_name, cc.cc_manager, f.cd_marital_status, f.cd_education_status ORDER BY Returns_Loss DESC
